description: My place is close to 168 Street Station. You’ll love my place because of the neighborhood, the comfy bed, and the ambiance. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers. If you choose my studio, you will have the entire studio to yourself.
name: Enjoy my private,cozy, and clean studio
review:
Overall a great experience. 2 min walk from the subway station. 'A' train will get you to time square in 15-20 mins. 

The room was clean and lots of products were left for us to help make the experience more comfortable and welcoming. 

Overall, a very good place to stay for tourists.
